###
FortiGate is a next-generation firewall (NGFW) that delivers industry‑leading enterprise security with full visibility and threat protection.

## Identify some key FortiGate features
- FortiGate models range from entry-level hardware appliances to high-end appliances  
- FortiGate-VM (virtual appliance) provides the same protection as physical appliances  
- Supports deployment in public and private cloud environments  
- Ensures FortiGate can fit seamlessly into any environment  
